textAfterTable: The Event of the Academic Year 2014-2015! Friday, March 6, 2015 Benedict College welcomed President Barack Obama Welcome to Benedict College Over the years, Benedict College has remained true to the mission of preparing students to be "powers for good" in society. While the history of the college has been spectacular, Benedict's future will surpass its past. You are invited to be a part of this bright future. Apply to Benedict. Be a part of the teaching, research and service that will be the hallmark of this great institution. Take a Campus Virtual Tour. This is a mobile friendly website.
